 families.','civilian_victims_pic/Amdekiros_Aregawi_Gebru.png','2024-07-21 16:43:52.178739','Central Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Adwa Town'),('06eaf836289745658e83043250df7209','Gidey Jebjeb','Male',50,'Tahtay Adiyabo, Shembelina (ወረዳ ታሕታይ ኣድያቦ ጣብያ ሸምበሊና)','Family Members and Relatives','Family Members and Relatives','Killed by Eritrean forces',NULL,'Killed by the Eritrean soldiers. He was a driver.','civilian_victims_pic/default.png','2024-10-13 14:55:20.683573','North Western Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Tahtay Adiyabo'),('06f826e2d19a49bcb934ddfceef57784','Welduhitsan Tadesse','Male',NULL,'Saharti Samre District, Cheli (ቸሊ )','Family Members and Relatives','Family Members and Relatives','Killed by Eritrean forces','2021-02-15','Killed by the Eritrean soldiers on February 15, 2021.','civilian_victims_pic/default.png','2024-06-21 19:20:23.421004','South Eastern Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Saharti'),('07149750d3134f1185d1414f3c45199c','Adhanom Gebreegziabher','Male',NULL,'Saharti Samre Distirct, Adi Esher (ሰሓርቲ፣ ቁሸት ዓዲ ዕሽር )','Family Members and Relatives','https://www.facebook.com/gebremeskel.gebremariam/posts/5042518405822949','Killed by Ethiopian and Eritrean forces',NULL,'Killed by the Ethiopian and Eritrean soldiers.','civilian_victims_pic/default.png','2024-04-29 23:18:06.770002','South Eastern Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Saharti'),('07203849b1d44dc68edef41f2b2ed255','Keshi Hadera Miruts (Priest)','Male',NULL,'Werei Leke, Kola Geblel','Family Members and Relatives, Tweet','Family Members and Relatives, https://twitter.com/HailuKebede_/status/1396422138635165697','Killed by Ethiopian and Eritrean forces',NULL,'Killed by the Ethiopian and Eritrean soldiers. He was a priest.','civilian_victims_pic/default.png','2024-07-20 21:13:51.310942','Central Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Mai Kinetal'),('07206218808c432fa17920b12d52897d','Tesfamariam Asgedom Mengesha','Male',60,'Adwa, Enda Mariam Shewito, Adi-Senay','Family Members and Relatives, T