 2021. He was killed when the federal police opened fire on civilians in the Axum market.','civilian_victims_pic/Solomon_Birhane_Asfaw.jpeg','2024-07-18 19:00:09.454422','Central Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Axum'),('70826e8837244f9194c813cb59f1645e','Asfaw Berhe (Deacon)','Male',NULL,'Axum','Family Members and Relatives','https://www.facebook.com/abaynesh.habtu/posts/3934271159968316','Killed by Eritrean forces',NULL,'Among the hundreds of civilians massacred in Axum by the Eritrean soldiers.','civilian_victims_pic/Asfaw_Berhe.jpg','2024-04-24 15:00:03.671507','Central Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Axum'),('70a321fc0140467f93b5136ea8928a84','Gebremichael Abadi','Male',NULL,'Negash Kushet Egrikaran, Wukro','Family Members and Relatives','https://www.facebook.com/elsa.desta','Killed by Eritrean forces','2020-11-24','Killed while fleeing with many others to escape from the indiscriminate attack of the Eritrean soldiers on November 24, 2020.','civilian_victims_pic/default.png','2024-04-03 17:30:49.886538','Eastern Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Kilte Awulaelo'),('70c7c0d37e1d450ca95da2844d85435f','Alganesh Guesh','Female',55,'Egela District, Gerhusernay','Family Members and Relatives','Family Members and Relatives','Killed by Ethiopian forces','2021-01-26','Alganesh was killed by Ethiopian soldiers who were members of the Ethiopian Northern Command, previously stationed in the Central Zone of Tigray. She was killed on January 26, 2021. Witnesses reported that the soldiers first cut off both of her breasts with a knife and then fatally stabbed her in the neck with machetes. They falsely accused her of involvement in the November 2020 operation of the Northern Command. Some of these soldiers were held captive by the Tigrayan Defense Forces (TDF), later pardoned, and released in early December 2020.','civilian_victims_pic/default_female.jpg','2024-05-02 15:36:45.476546','Central Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Egela'),('70e7ac8d62754d86af1efc76544e4e29','Geb