g with three of his brothers (Gebremedhin Araya, Kibrom Araya, and Gueshaya Araya).  According to witnesses cited by the Telegraph, the three brothers were shot and their bodies were subsequently dumped in a nearby crater. It took five days for their father, Araya Gebretekle, and his eldest son, Mebrahten Araya, to locate the bodies of their loved ones.','civilian_victims_pic/default.png','2024-06-08 17:51:48.862277','Central Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Abiy Addi'),('a1dfcb3616e84960a1f5627a87b14f0c','Milat Kalyou Birhane (with three of her siblings)','Female',NULL,'Kilte Awulaelo District, Debre Tsion, Debre Mear(ጣብያ ደብረ ፅዮን ቁሸት ደብረ መዓር )','Family Members and Relatives','https://www.facebook.com/genet.welday.9655','Killed by Eritrean forces','2020-11-25','Killed from heavy artillery shelling around Hawzen by the Eritrean soldiers on November 25, 2020. She was killed along with three of her siblings, Shushay Kalyou Birhane, Michael Kalyou Birhane, and Samrawit Kalyou Birhane.','civilian_victims_pic/Milat_Kalyou_Birhane.jpeg','2024-07-22 19:43:49.164324','Eastern Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Kilte Awulaelo'),('a1e8a2c676034075a0943f26e884136b','Gebrekiros Guesh','Male',NULL,'Tanqua Abergele, Yechila, Jijike (ጣብያ ጅጅቀ)','Family Members and Relatives','Family Members and Relatives','Killed by Ethiopian forces','2020-12-05','Killed by the Ethiopian soldiers on December 05, 2020. He was a farmer.','civilian_victims_pic/default.png','2024-07-12 13:11:14.146738','Central Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Yechila Abergele'),('a1e9854d0c844017b4511dd5e4d4c8e4','Alemtsehay Gidey','Female',NULL,'Abuna Yemata Guh, Debre Selam, Hawzen','Family Members and Relatives','Family Members and Relatives','Killed by Ethiopian forces','2021-05-08','Killed by the Eritrean soldiers on May 08, 2021.','civilian_victims_pic/default_female.jpg','2024-07-14 13:33:54.922102','Eastern Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Hawzen'),('a1f240205631460093f94d3f616139ff','Gueshom Abay','Male',NUL