evelopment/2023/apr/20/the-hyenas-had-eaten-the-rest-survivors-speak-about-the-horrors-of-massacres-in-northern-tigray','Killed by Eritrean forces',NULL,'Tiebe Yihdego Gebreegziabher was among the civilians massacred around Mariam Shewito by the Eritrean forces. She was killed along with her 5-year-old daughter, Weyni Tsegay Weldu.','civilian_victims_pic/default_female.jpg','2024-10-12 19:40:55.616569','Central Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Adwa'),('ffe83c0d156a405d9b7c70b5b4ad5e37','Tesfay Bayru','Male',65,'Adi Gudem, Mai Haidi (ማይ ሃይዲ)','Family Members and Relatives','Family Members and Relatives','Killed by Ethiopian forces','2021-04-11','Tesfay was killed (stoned to death) by Ethiopian soldiers on April 11, 2021. He was carrying a new mother, who had recently given birth, from DaEreta (ዳዕሬታ) to the Adi Gudem (ዓዲ ጉደም) clinic.','civilian_victims_pic/default.png','2024-06-09 13:56:26.931893','South Eastern Tigray',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'Hintalo');
