Mekelle University in Mekelle. The drones were deployed by the Ethiopian government of Abiy Ahmed. © 2021 Private','photo_archive/Mekelle_Diaspora1.jpeg','2024-04-29 19:18:00.639099',0,63,'Mekelle Town'),('15242d8784ad4809a896857241c33f5d','Mekelle, Diaspora Neighborhood','2021-11-26','On November 26, 2021, a drone strike targeted a residential neighborhood known as \'Diaspora\' near the Veterinary Campus of Mekelle University in Mekelle. The drones were deployed by the Ethiopian government of Abiy Ahmed. © 2021 Private','photo_archive/Mekelle_Diaspora13.jpeg','2024-04-29 19:24:41.670087',0,63,'Mekelle Town'),('17842bc07c9f42bc9f82ff26c9232fda','Naeder',NULL,'Debris from a missile lies in the backyard of a destroyed house in Naeder. © 2024 Shewit Wudassie','photo_archive/Naeder-house1.jpeg','2024-04-27 14:41:29.367687',0,63,'Naeder'),('1a76d66568f74dccbb9836c60e6016f6','Mekelle University, Adi-Haki Campus','2022-09-13','Footage of a drone strike targeting the Adi-Haki Campus of Mekelle University on September 13, 2022. The drones responsible were deployed by the Ethiopian government of Abiy Ahmed. © 2022 Private','photo_archive/MU_AdiHaki_Campus3.jpeg','2024-04-29 22:36:14.811793',0,63,'Mekelle Town'),('204b292f257346cbb2d36debdc0a3789','Embaseneyti ',NULL,'A destroyed Secondary School in the district of Embaseneyti. © Tigray Education Bureau','photo_archive/Embasenyti2.jpg','2024-04-26 19:20:03.770470',0,63,'Emba Seneyti'),('22d94063ac9343b4942da1f6b4a034fe','Embaseneyti ',NULL,'A destroyed Secondary School in the district of Embaseneyti. © Tigray Education Bureau','photo_archive/Embasenyti1.jpg','2024-04-26 19:19:32.734065',0,63,'Emba Seneyti'),('2441f9ea5dac40ad938b53399ccb6360','Fatsi',NULL,'Photo footage shows the aftermath of an attack on the Fatsi City administration building in the Woreda of Gulomekeda by Eritrean soldiers. The windows are broken, the walls are heavily damaged, and the furniture is burned. © 2024 Shewit Wudassie','photo_archive/Fatsi-Administration4.jpeg','2024-05-02 13:52:08.423464',0,63,'Gulo Mekeda'),('24ac44562de64d5594959d8b1ac4931d','Debre Abay',NULL,'Anti-Tigrayan graffiti is displayed on the walls of a vandalized room in a health center in Debre Abay. © AP (Source: https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/apr/02/ethiopia-1900-people-killed-in-massacres-in-tigray-identified)','photo_archive/looted_health_center_in_Debre_Abay.avif','2024-06-06 19:37:36.465850',0,63,'Sheraro'),('274d1a9c1dd84e6bad3464cf6725fc9c','Fatsi',NULL,'Photo footage shows the aftermath of an attack on the Fatsi City administration building in the Woreda of Gulomekeda by Eritrean soldiers. The windows are broken, the walls are heavily damaged, the furniture is burned,  and paper files and documents can also be seen thrown and scattered on the ground. © 2024 Shewit Wudassie','photo_archive/Fatsi-Administration6.jpeg','2024-05-02 13:53:34.994050',0,63,'Gulo Mekeda'),('29a1f1b5d62c4f19a6c07085f5844737','Adwa',NULL,'A completely destroyed and looted textile factory in Adwa, Almeda, by the Eritrean soldiers. © 2020 Private','photo_archive/Almeda-Textile-5.jpeg','2024-04-21 23:47:05.213425',0,63,'Adwa Town'),('2e15384adf8b4771b14c447031a4e1b4','Mekelle, Diaspora Neighborhood','2021-11-26','On November 26, 2021, a drone strike targeted a residential neighborhood known as \'Diaspora\' near the Veterinary Campus of Mekelle University in Mekelle. The drones were deployed by the Ethiopian government of Abiy Ahmed. © 2021 Private','photo_archive/Mekelle_Diaspora9.jpeg','2024-04-29 19:22:37.384654',0,63,'Mekelle Town'),('2e5c9c6f04b04e9b8420bd09af794bea','Mekelle, Diaspora Neighborhood','2021-11-26','On November 26, 2021, a drone strike targeted a residential neighborhood known as \'Diaspora\' near the Veterinary Campus of Mekelle University in Mekelle. The drones were deployed by the Ethiopian government of Abiy Ahmed. © 2021 Private','photo_archive/Mekelle_Diaspora10.jpeg','2024-04-29 19:23:10.586065',0,63,'Mekelle Town'),('2fecdc0cea784